  "text": "The motifs and domains present in the SSU processome proteins were identified using the SCOP Superfamily (http:// supfam.org/SUPERFAMILY/index.html) [CITATION_1] , the MIPS Comprehensive Yeast Genome Database (http://mips.helmholtzmuenchen.de/genre/proj/yeast/) [CITATION_2] , Pfam domains (http:// pfam.sanger.ac.uk/) [CITATION_3] , PROSITE (http://ca.expasy.org/ prosite/) [CITATION_4] , SMART (http://smart.embl-heidelberg.de/) [CITATION_5] and the Conserved Domain Database at NCBI (http://www.ncbi. nlm.nih.gov/Structure/cdd/wrpsb.cgi) [CITATION_6] .",
