      "citation_id": "[CITATION_6]",
      "span_text": "The motifs and domains present in the SSU processome proteins were identified using the SCOP Superfamily (http:// supfam.org/SUPERFAMILY/index.html), the MIPS Comprehensive Yeast Genome Database (http://mips.helmholtzmuenchen.de/genre/proj/yeast/), Pfam domains (http:// pfam.sanger.ac.uk/), PROSITE (http://ca.expasy.org/ prosite/), SMART (http://smart.embl-heidelberg.de/) and the Conserved Domain Database at NCBI (http://www.ncbi. nlm.nih.gov/Structure/cdd/wrpsb.cgi)"
